### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### LOCAL TESTING (cds watch)
### http://localhost:4004
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### 1. Get All People (from TripPin)
GET http://localhost:4004/trip/People
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Get Status Values (from SQLite/HANA)
GET http://localhost:4004/trip/StatusValues
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Get All Custom Data (from SQLite/HANA)
GET http://localhost:4004/trip/CustomData
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Create Person
### → Creates in TripPin
### → Saves comments + status to SQLite/HANA
POST http://localhost:4004/trip/createPerson
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userName" : "PCTEST4",
    "firstName": "PC",
    "lastName" : "CH",
    "gender"   : "Male",
    "email"    : "john@example.com",
    "comments" : "CHECK",
    "status"   : "Active"
}

###

### 5. Get Person Details (Combined)
### → TripPin data + SQLite/HANA custom data
GET http://localhost:4004/trip/getPersonDetails(userName='PCTEST3')
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Update Custom Data only (SQLite/HANA)
POST http://localhost:4004/trip/updateCustomData
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userName": "johndoe999",
    "comments": "Updated comment locally",
    "status"  : "Pending"
}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════
### BTP PRODUCTION TESTING
### Replace with your actual BTP URL
### ═══════════════════════════════════════

### 7. Get Token first from:
### POST https://YOUR-TRIAL.authentication.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/oauth/token
### grant_type=client_credentials
### client_id=YOUR_CLIENT_ID
### client_secret=YOUR_CLIENT_SECRET

### 8. Get All People (BTP)
GET https://trip-app-srv.cfapps.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/trip/People
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 9. Create Person (BTP)
POST https://trip-app-srv.cfapps.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/trip/createPerson
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "userName" : "btpuser001",
    "firstName": "BTP",
    "lastName" : "User",
    "gender"   : "Male",
    "email"    : "btpuser@example.com",
    "comments" : "Created on BTP",
    "status"   : "Active"
}

###

### 10. Get Person Details (BTP)
GET https://trip-app-srv.cfapps.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/trip/getPersonDetails(userName='btpuser001')
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 11. Update Custom Data (BTP)
POST https://trip-app-srv.cfapps.eu10.hana.ondemand.com/trip/updateCustomData
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
    "userName": "btpuser001",
    "comments": "Updated on BTP",
    "status"  : "Closed"
}
